sc_cat_item_producer.description:
Certificate Request

Provides X509 Certificate to support multiple security use cases including encryption, digital signatures, or Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) technology. Use this form to request Certificates for both internally and externally facing applications.

Certificate can be used to provide

  • Authentication
  • Authorization
  • Non-Repudiation
  • Integrity
  • Confidentiality

Terms & Conditions

  • May be subject to CAB review
  • May be subject to Freeze Calendar restrictions
  • Estimated turnaround time is 10 business days
  • Dependency, CSR must be attached if applicable

Questions

  • If you have questions or need additional assistance, please call the Service Desk at x4HELP or 1-877-864-7979.
  • If you are unsure of what options to select on this request or need immediate attention on a certificate request please contact DL Certificate Management.

Please Note:  External Certificates could take up to a week to complete depending on type and selections.  Please plan accordingly.
